  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Sporthotel Panorama is on a half board basis.</p>
<p>Each morning enjoy a buffet breakfast in the hotel's restaurant with a hot menu cooked to order.</p>
<p>In the evening you'll get a four-course meal with different choices and on Friday's there's a buffet of delicious starters. The hotel hosts a weekly gala dinner, which is a great chance to sample some of the delicious local dishes followed by an aperitivo in the bar with a DJ.</p>
<p>The hotel has a separate A La Carte restaurant, the Stua Ladina, which you can pay locally to dine in.</p>
<p>Christmas and New Year gala dinners are included.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
