  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Col Alto Rooms </strong>are about 28m² and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed). Double or Austrian twin* beds available. They have mountain views from the balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Panoramic Rooms </strong>are about 28m² and sleep up to four people. They're south facing and have a balcony. </p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms </strong>are about 18m² and have a balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Panoramic Suites </strong>are all located in the main building. They're spacious at about 50m² and sleep up to four people (extra bed is a double sofa bed). They're south facing with a balcony. </p>
<p>*Austrian twin beds are one double bed frame with two single mattresses and two single duvet covers. Austrian twin beds are limited and must be specified at the time of booking but cannot be guaranteed. </p>
<p><strong>Bedroom facilities</strong></p>
